Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========OP================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:53.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:01:01.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:25.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:32.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:48.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:57.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:13.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:53.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上这一带视野最美的那颗树
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:01:01.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子笑了 笑得天真无邪 她看到了梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:25.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,定定地盯着空中畅游的鱼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:32.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小镇每个角落里渐渐褪色的日子浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,拉钩上吊百年不变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,即使分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:48.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,等待约定实现的心情也寄托在这颗树上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一遍一遍地重复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:57.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都止不住泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来又继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是要印证这一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:13.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,山间回音响不绝 你说是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========Story================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓一大堆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么螺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是田螺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是田螺呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有好多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 收集到大量丰年虾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到蝌蚪虾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到一大堆
Comment: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,(title)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:18.49,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H4BB5EF&\pos(1117.5,920)}做\N了\N晴\N雨\N娃\N娃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 喜欢蝌蚪虾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到 很稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次照顾它们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大家轮班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是完全由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜欢蝌蚪虾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在下雨呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 今天忘记带雨伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 遮我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那…前辈 要不我来遮你到巴士站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 那拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才要请前辈多多指教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点出梅就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨也不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明明天是星期天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望明天是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行车要送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买给你了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶寄过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点迟 是入学贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样大家就能一起骑自行车去玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时先不要自己一个人骑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找人陪着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等雨停了就练习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要练习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨不停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不会停的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑不了自行车了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 做好晴雨娃娃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过总感觉和我想象中的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小一个 太阳公公不会找到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱对晴雨娃娃也很认真呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到好办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有纸碟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像餐具柜的抽屉里面有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用来做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先在纸碟上开条缝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用画笔沿着线涂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在这里缠上橡皮筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 之前买的白色雨衣还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在玄关哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳公公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我成为了晴雨娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我做得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样出去走一圈可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还在下雨 还是不要去了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是要出去 认认真真祈求太阳公公快点出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求晴天是晴雨娃娃的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那… 只能在我们家附近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小青蛙呀小青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小青蛙是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝌蚪是小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后腿出来花钱养
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前腿出来叛逆期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小青蛙呀小青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨天挖土好容易呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要造座山 再做条河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输给小铲子的诱惑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 用这个铲子敲水桶发出声音的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳公公会更容易发现我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳爷爷 太阳公公 快出来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么也不停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话看来要变成持久战了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣沾上黑色了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不好好工作不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 把莲华忘记拿的漫画送回去的路上 突然就下起雨来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有带雨伞就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像听到了什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在流黑眼泪和黑口水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪吗 这大白天的都会出现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算是妖怪也有好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能放过我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然离很远看不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它拿着什么武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎怎怎怎怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然拿着武器那肯定是坏妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去莲华家找穗姐帮忙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找准时机…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小小鞠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来和我一起祈求天晴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边说着什么一边挥着武器追过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺激了它的斗争心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨越下越大了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该去接莲酱回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了 莲酱的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗姐 救命 外面有妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救救救命呀 天照大神如来佛祖太阳公公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 不是坏妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着我也变成晴雨娃娃的话莲酱会高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠害怕得哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有哭呢 那是雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴雨娃娃的效果出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要练习骑自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日记 日记 日记记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该吃饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我要写观察日记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦 莲酱是蝌蚪虾负责人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 蝌蚪虾有长大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只吃了很多饲料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 这只游泳很快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有起名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪只呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个快点 巴士要来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的学也上完了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得出太阳了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了晴雨娃娃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起就害怕 求别说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那个星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱打扮成晴雨娃娃的样子在外面走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了晴天努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太努力了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去卖零食的那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去吧 刚好带零用钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑自行车去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会骑了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音好怀念呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖果拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖零食的也做晴雨娃娃了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨太无聊了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然做到一半雨就停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种花叫做紫斑风铃草哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫斑风铃草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是属于萤的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs48}紫斑风铃草日语为ホタルブクロ，日语汉字写做“蛍袋”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 吃晚饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去卖零食的那了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭的时候不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午才开始上学就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 说了不要拉我衣服了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤做完作业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海有做作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我有带作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然好可怜 不过也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝌蚪虾好像寿命很短的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华 下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水缸之后再收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 打开问题集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也下课了下课了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨不停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天星期天 大家再一起出去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呢 玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱想做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我漏了点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 巴士要来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海前辈没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人迟了一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 小心点呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是田地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啦 明天天晴的话要不要去抓蝌蚪虾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了很不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近好像开了家便利店 要不要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像要走两小时左右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 那不是很远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也就那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华也去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就明天下午吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小平先生去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太坑了 昨天的便利店远足太坑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 还在说那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遗憾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便利店还会关门开什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是24小时营业呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都收拾好了 为什么水缸还在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再靠近点看看怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么在里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是生出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我之前在想 蝌蚪虾会不会产卵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就把养虾的土放回去再加好水了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是小平先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 是小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,400)}小平先生出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多小平先生
